    &lt;/iframe&gt;</content><category term="van build"></category></entry><entry><title>Cedar Van Wall</title><link href="https://vanomad.com/cedar-van-wall.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2020-12-25T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2021-09-12T21:47:04-07:00</updated><author><name>vanomad</name></author><id>tag:vanomad.com,2020-12-25:/cedar-van-wall.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image of finished cedar van wall" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZUAymXZHAMlhfHLWOmR98SbpUt1wjkGv3pka&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;I started of with a large piece of paper to make a template.  I used painters tape to hold up the paper and pencil to help trace out the curves and edges undernith. then I cut with sissors untile I got a good fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image making paper template" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZAAymXZRAXMdcfIsEkTMuX2hhhbejE6jQLy&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The part of the paper template extending over the side door.
&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZaAymXZry94YIAlEqJ5WFyrqsr8EmWT9f97&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;View of the side door and wheel well.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZ3AymXZoKFt9SuhrO0bcsWjeUAbehVslQQ7&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;View of the paper template over the wheel well and along the back door.  I had to ape in some extra pater to fill the gap.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZGAymXZADEa9dLlVSpH5mmvy5SLkbNCEtpV&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now it is time to transfer the paper template to the cardboard template. We transfer to a cardboard template because it is more rigid and will emulate the actual ply wood wall better then paper.  therefore giving a more accurate model.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZvAymXZN9RbBLJqnmjxg59EaRo6kL5RVqx7&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once I trace out the template with pencil onto the cardboard, I then use a box cutter to cut out the cardboard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZiAymXZHnBA6WBUnwutqkLBdx1UEmVKj7CX&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the cardboard template cut out I can check how it fits and make any adjustments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZoAymXZ7awzaYVND7F4NnUxoERT4mlJUxLy&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It turns out I do need to trim some cardbaord to get a better fit around the angles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZ0NymXZKYtvD1V4wcYUOlQ4f2pmlVczenFk&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZpNymXZmKOVUjcWO1FtR4MQKfiyNzxlyrWy&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZzNymXZ6amooeaxEMk1y88PzxOkKjV9bkHX&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the cardboard template done, I tranfered it to the ply wood and cut the plywood with a jigsaw.  Now I am going to glue the cedar to the ply wood using liquid nails.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZ4NymXZgRS1O4H0ShBAFmTDA6YvRyyNQpby&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image" src="https://api.pcloud.com/getpubthumb?code=XZhNymXZ6Pq72OveD5YNgJTacuMzlu3C0JHX&amp;amp;linkpassword=undefined&amp;amp;size=700x700&amp;amp;crop=0&amp;amp;type=autok"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
